cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and word embeddings. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it discusses the use of machine learning systems and the potential societal harm they can cause. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it addresses the societal implications of biased machine learning systems. Finally, it could be classified under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as it deals with the analysis of large corpora of text data.
